data.description: Don't wait any longer or this one will be GONE! Move In Ready featuring bright, spacious open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, newer A/C, newer interior paint, beautiful wood floors, and ceiling fans throughout. The fully remodeled kitchen offers new quartz counters, new stainless appliances, newly painted cabinets, new lighting and new tile flooring. There is plenty of countertop & cabinet space, pantry, eat in kitchen and breakfast bar! Fully remodeled Primary bathroom features full tile walk in shower, quartz top dual vanity and new tile flooring. $13K in beautifully redesigned backyard w/ covered patio, extended patio concrete & pavers, and a large synthetic turf lawn, green all year to enjoy! Seller will contribute $5K towards buyer's closing costs or rate buy down! Welcome Home!
